== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Moscou mu [[Burusiya]] kuri se wo muri [[Tanzaniya]] na nyina [[Uburusiya|w'Uburusiya]]. Igihe yari afite imyaka 5, umuryango we wimukiye muri [[Tanzaniya]].<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5275929/</ref>  Amaze kuba i Dar es Salaam, muri [[Tanzaniya]] imyaka 14 na Los Angeles imyaka 8, kuri ubu yimukiye i Stockholm, muri [[Suwede]].<ref>http://www.scandinaviantalentsindia.com/ernest-napoleon/index.html</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 3, yakinnye bwa mbere mu ikinamico ya Noheri yise ''Umwaka mushya muri'' ''New Year's in the old Soviet Union''. Igihe yari muri [[Tanzaniya]], yakoraga kuri EATV<ref>https://thoselondonchicks.com/chicks-chat-with-ernest-napoleon-not-till-end-of-month/</ref>, televiziyo nini muri [[Afurika]] y'Iburasirazuba icyo gihe. Yakinnye kandi nkumu DJ muri 'Club Billicanas', club izwi cyane muri [[Afrika]] aho yabaye umuhanzi ufata amajwi ya Bongo Flava, injyana yumuziki muri [[Afrika]] yuburasirazuba. Yakoreyeyo ku izina rya 'MC Napo'<ref>https://www.thecitizen.co.tz/tanzania/magazines/the-beat/meet-the-brain-behind-going-bongo-2541686</ref>. 

Ernest akiri ingimbi, yimukiye i Los Angeles ahabwa impamyabumenyi ya mudasobwa. Hanyuma yize gukina no kwandika imyaka 7 akiri i Los Angeles. Abifashijwemo n'inshuti na bagenzi be, yakoze filime ye ya mbere ya ''Going Bongo'' <ref>https://justcelebritymag.com/2015/05/15/exclusive-interview-with-going-bongo-star-ernest-napoleon/</ref>.  Iyi filime yatewe inkunga n'ubuzima bw'abaganga babaga mu Bwongereza, Dr Lewis Burger, <ref>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/evewoman/amp/my-man/article/2000183314/ernest-napoleon-the-bongo-magician</ref> aho Ernest yakinnye. <ref>https://goingbongo.tumblr.com/post/55008667419/actors-ernest-napoleon-as-dr-lewis-burger-and#.X52JGPjPzIU</ref> Filime ye ifatwa nka firime ya mbere mpuzamahanga yakozwe na Tanzaniya ndetse na film ya mbere yo muri Afrika yuburasirazuba yemerwa na iTunes.  <ref>http://thoselondonchicks.com/chicks-chat-with-ernest-napoleon-not-till-end-of-month/</ref>

Muri 2017, yakoze film ''Kiumeni'' yafatiwe i Dar es Salaam. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza nyuma iza gutsindira ibihembo bibiri mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Zanzibar .  Niwe washinze inzu itanga umusaruro, ''Enigma Pictures'' . Muri 2017, yagizwe perezida wa 'D Street Media Group', isosiyete mpuzamahanga ikora no gukwirakwiza. <ref>https://edaily.co.ke/entertainment/top-east-african-producer-joins-us-based-media-group-as-president-125394/enews/eworld/</ref> Yakoze kandi TV Series ''Mother City'' na firime ya gatatu ''Peponi'' . Muri icyo gihe, yafatanyije gukora filime yo mu [[Bwongereza]] ''Reka Ntamuntu Umenye'' izenguruka inkuru yukuri ivuga ku mugaragu wâ€™umunyamerika. <ref>https://www.cine.com/actores/ernest-napoleon</ref>

